349
00:19:22,361 --> 00:19:24,361
Apa dia sungguh mengambilnya?

350
00:19:24,361 --> 00:19:25,561
Dan dia bilang, "Aku menyimpannya di apartemenku,

351
00:19:25,561 --> 00:19:27,461
