352
00:19:27,461 --> 00:19:29,461
Di mana? Apartemennya!

353
00:19:30,861 --> 00:19:32,361
Conan!

354
00:19:32,361 --> 00:19:35,861
Aku berhasil mendapatkan kunci utama dari tuan tanahnya!

355
00:19:37,261 --> 00:19:38,761
Hei!

356
00:19:38,761 --> 00:19:40,561
Conan!

357
00:19:40,561 --> 00:19:41,761
-Apakah ini kamarnya? -Yah.

358
00:19:42,861 --> 00:19:44,861
Di mana? Di mana?

359
00:19:44,861 --> 00:19:47,161
Di mana? Di mana? Di mana?

360
00:19:47,161 --> 00:19:49,061
Di mana catatanku?

